01:32:33,700 --> 01:32:36,220
 So I think a lot of the fear

1562
01:32:36,220 --> 01:32:39,260
 of the upsetting of the social order,

1563
01:32:39,260 --> 01:32:40,940
 I think it's what drive, you know,

1564
01:32:40,940 --> 01:32:44,820
 some Chinese Christian or other ethnic Christian

1565
01:32:44,820 --> 01:32:46,580
 to support Trump.

