01:32:46,580 --> 01:32:47,540
 - Yes, yes.

1567
01:32:47,540 --> 01:32:48,380
 Thank you for that.

1568
01:32:48,380 --> 01:32:49,580
 I think that's true.

1569
01:32:49,580 --> 01:32:50,420
 I agree.

1570
01:32:50,420 --> 01:32:53,260
 - I don't know if,

1571
01:32:53,260 --> 01:32:56,340
 I don't think I can speak for a lot of people,

