01:33:02,620 --> 01:33:08,860
 because of the way that he's so strong

1575
01:33:08,860 --> 01:33:13,780
 against some governments,

1576
01:33:13,780 --> 01:33:14,620
 such as

1577
01:33:18,020 --> 01:33:18,860
 CCP.

