01:33:23,020 --> 01:33:24,620
 And also in America,

1580
01:33:24,620 --> 01:33:28,540
 I don't know if I get it right,

1581
01:33:28,540 --> 01:33:31,380
 but the Christian, the Bible belt

1582
01:33:31,380 --> 01:33:36,380
 is also where the Rust Belt is, roughly.

1583
01:33:36,380 --> 01:33:39,300
 And before Trump's era,

1584
01:33:39,300 --> 01:33:42,020
 a lot of the jobs were lost to countries

1585
01:33:42,020 --> 01:33:44,260
 like Mexico and China.

1586
01:33:44,260 --> 01:33:47,260
 So a lot of people have lost their jobs.

1587
01:33:47,260 --> 01:33:52,260
 So maybe partly why they want to make America great again

1588
01:33:52,260 --> 01:33:55,380
 is such that jobs could come back to them,

1589
01:33:55,380 --> 01:34:00,380
 so that such that they can actually have their jobs back.

1590
01:34:00,380 --> 01:34:02,860
 I think that could be partly why.

1591
01:34:02,860 --> 01:34:05,540
 - I agree with that as well.

1592
01:34:05,540 --> 01:34:06,900
 Yeah, yeah.

